            . I am a <rs id="t18150405-139-viclabel765" type="occupation">plaisterer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-139-victim1189 t18150405-139-viclabel765"></join>; I live at Battle-bridge. On the 22nd of February, near three in the morning, in Holborn, I met with the prisoner, she asked me to go home with her; I was not perfectly sober. I walked up <placeName id="t18150405-139-crimeloc766">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150405-139-crimeloc766" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18150405-139-crimeloc766" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-139-off763 t18150405-139-crimeloc766"></join> with her as far as <placeName id="t18150405-139-crimeloc767">Gray's-inn-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150405-139-crimeloc767" type="placeName" value="Gray's-inn-lane"></interp>
